### 5. CONTACT (`/contacto`)

**Contact Form**
Fields:
- Nombre completo (required)
- Email (required)
- Teléfono (required)
- Asunto (dropdown): Regularización 2026 | Arraigo | Nacionalidad | Otro
- Mensaje (textarea)
- Checkbox: "Acepto la política de privacidad" (required)
- Submit button: "Enviar mensaje"

**Contact Info Sidebar**
- Phone: +34 XXX XXX XXX
- WhatsApp: Same number with click-to-chat
- Email: info@pombohorowitz.com
- Office addresses

**Map**
- Google Maps embed of Madrid office

---

## Components to Build

1. `<Header />` — Logo, nav links, language toggle (ES/EN), mobile hamburger
2. `<Footer />` — As described above
3. `<CTABanner />` — Reusable gold banner with headline + button
4. `<BlogCard />` — Image, title, date, excerpt, link
5. `<ServiceCard />` — Icon, title, description, link
6. `<TeamMember />` — Photo, name, title, bio
7. `<ContactForm />` — With validation and submission handling
8. `<FAQAccordion />` — Expandable Q&A items
9. `<TrustBar />` — Horizontal strip of credentials/badges

---

## SEO Requirements

**Meta Tags (per page)**
- title, description, og:title, og:description, og:image
- Canonical URLs
- hreflang for ES/EN versions

**Schema Markup**
- Organization (LegalService)
- LocalBusiness for each office
- BlogPosting for articles
- FAQPage for FAQ sections

**Sitemap**
- Auto-generated sitemap.xml
- Submit to Google Search Console

**Robots.txt**
- Allow all except /api/

---

## Performance Requirements

- Lighthouse score > 90 on all metrics
- Images: WebP format, lazy loading, responsive srcset
- Fonts: Subset and preload
- No external scripts except analytics

---

## Deployment Checklist

1. [ ] Set up Vercel project
2. [ ] Connect pombohorowitz.com domain
3. [ ] Configure environment variables (analytics IDs, form endpoints)
4. [ ] Set up redirects (www → non-www)
5. [ ] SSL certificate (automatic via Vercel)
6. [ ] Test contact form submission
7. [ ] Submit sitemap to Google Search Console
8. [ ] Install Meta Pixel
9. [ ] Test mobile responsiveness
10. [ ] Test language toggle (if implementing EN version)

---

## Notes for Claude Code

- Start with the homepage and regularización page — these are highest priority
- Blog can use static MDX files, no need for a CMS
- Contact form should email to info@pombohorowitz.com
- Don't overthink the design — clean, professional, navy + gold palette
- The tuspapeles2026.es CTA should be VERY prominent on the regularización page
- Mobile-first approach

---

